data.description: Beautiful Well maintained one and a half story home in lake community, 3 to 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, office, three living areas, formal dining, large kitchen with island, screened-in porch. 3-car garage. Lots of upgrades,Split bedroom design with master downstairs featuring a large walk in closet, comfortable Drees floor plan. Community has two pools, clubhouse, exercise facility, walking trails and fountain lakes. Mansfield school district
